  <brief_title>Ceramic-on-Ceramic Total Hip Arthroplasty and Squeaking: Influence of Component Design</brief_title>
  <official_title>Ceramic-on-Ceramic Total Hip Arthroplasty and Squeaking: A Prospective, Blinded, Randomized Clinical Trial of Influence of Component Design</official_title>
  <sponsors>
